definition: abbr. for Xinjiang 新疆[Xin1 jiang1] or Singapore 新加坡[Xin1 jia1 po1]/surname Xin
to be born/to give birth/life/to grow/raw/uncooked/student

sentences.english: Conclusion The incident rate of ARF was high in asphyxia neonatorum.

sentences.english: A newborn is ready to bond to its parents.
